# Line ending policy
# - Keep LF in the repository for text files.
# - Use CRLF only for Windows-native scripts.

* text=auto eol=lf

*.bat text eol=crlf
*.cmd text eol=crlf
*.ps1 text eol=crlf

# Binary assets
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.spv binary
*.ico binary
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
*.lib binary
